{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2a58fed62c","title":"关于“农民生活苦”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"268278eb1f","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"2a58fed62c"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"0c83e4d466","name":"周兴润"},{"id":"1b39e05593","name":"薛书云"},{"id":"3786d2fe2e","name":"罗蕴芳"},{"id":"477cd312f3","name":"程小敏"},{"id":"914865708e","name":"孙澜"},{"id":"978cadaa11","name":"杨冠五"},{"id":"bdcd383dc0","name":"刘田生"},{"id":"ea25ac8f66","name":"西北农学院"},{"id":"f08f6c9fd4","name":"张君盈"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c1efb7c8df","type":"title","text":"关于“农民生活苦”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2a58fed62c"},{"id":"dbbfb9b0da","type":"authors","text":"西北农学院张君盈罗蕴芳刘田生程小敏周兴润孙澜薛书云杨嗣云","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2a58fed62c"},{"id":"ba6ba20ea8","type":"paragraph","text":"1．“合作化害的人不能活了，每人一天一斤粮，我们那里多半为杂粮，农民生活很苦。”(化59级学生　张君盈)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2a58fed62c"},{"id":"fc7453bb3e","type":"paragraph","text":"2．“报纸上登合作化优越性的照片，不见得符合实际情况，还不是找几个典型来的。”(林58级学生　罗蕴芳)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2a58fed62c"},{"id":"f122b656cd","type":"paragraph","text":"3．“农民生活太苦了。”(水58级学生　刘田生)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2a58fed62c"},{"id":"24b264b718","type":"paragraph","text":"4．“我国农民生活苦的要命，如果在别的国家，农民一定会起来暴动的。”(农60级学生　程小敏)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2a58fed62c"},{"id":"7cf92490f0","type":"paragraph","text":"5．“邓小平的报告说，山西农民生活提高了，农民都买了自行车，实际上不是这样，因为政府硬要农民将钱存在银行，农民不存都买了自行车。”(水58级学生  周兴润)","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2a58fed62c"},{"id":"f2bcacc19c","type":"paragraph","text":"6．“解放后农民生活并没有提高，但喜欢腐化。”(植60级学生　吕庆仕)","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2a58fed62c"},{"id":"00d8c9c4c4","type":"paragraph","text":"7．“农民生活很苦，农产品的收购价格低，而制成工业成品涨价后，高价的卖给农民，这是一种变象的剥削。土改后，农民的生活仍然很苦，而地主还是照样的有吃有喝，因为地主过去有上学的，现在又是干部，那怕什么？”(无名)","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2a58fed62c"},{"id":"2ea44683ac","type":"paragraph","text":"17．“农民生活很苦，绝大多数都吃南瓜。”(无名)","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2a58fed62c"},{"id":"60b1c0ea9c","type":"paragraph","text":"18．“农民生活苦，粮食不够吃，反正够不够三百六。”(林59级学生　薛书云)","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2a58fed62c"},{"id":"b67617da07","type":"paragraph","text":"19．“现在农村生活苦得要死、我永不如解放前了。”(经60级学生　杨嗣云)","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2a58fed62c"},{"id":"5a5a325433","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《西北农学院右派言论及错误言论汇集》(西北农学院马列主义教研组编印，1957年12月)。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2a58fed62c"}],"page":{"id":"eb1a88c2e5","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2a58fed62c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}